D3 Security System App for Custom Alert Action

-------------------------------------------------------
## Introduction:

This App sends events captured by alert to D3 Security System 

-------------------------------------------------------
## Installation and Setup

- In Splunk, navigate to the app manager page. Click "Install app from file" and upload the D3 App.
- Navigate to app manager page, click "Set up" on "D3 Alert Action" row. Fill out all configuration settings and click "Save". 

-------------------------------------------------------
